Bump version, merge Steven Farlie's fix and add him to README
Use FFI to determine platform-dependent library name
Prepare for ruby-llvm-2.9.2. Add ruby-llvm-support shared library to provide functionality missing in llvm-c. Library is built during gem install.
Add Ary Manzana to the list of contributors.
Using Gem::PackageTask instead of deprecated Rake::GemPackageTask

API simplification

* new() is preferred as the public constructor
* ExecutionEngine.create_jit_compiler is now JITCompiler.new

Fix bug casting between double <=> GenericValue

* Replace LLVM.GenericValue(value) with LLVM.make_generic_value(type, value)
* Add LLVM::GenericValue.from_d for creating a GenericValue representing a double
